messages-description =
    A Matrix messages widget for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    Displays recent messages and unread room counts from the user's Matrix account
    on the local Tuwunel server. Shows room name, sender avatar, and a message preview.
    Clicking a room opens the full conversation in the FreeSynergy Browser.

messages-features =
    - Recent messages from all Matrix rooms
    - Unread message count per room
    - Sender avatar and message preview
    - Click-to-open in FreeSynergy Browser
    - Powered by the local Tuwunel (Matrix) server
